E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Why do you stand out in the open. Hide yourself, you idiot.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~你怎么傻愣在外面。躲起来啊，你个傻逼。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~~c~ I think Mr. Lopez will kick your ass tomorrow.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~~c~我觉得Lopez先生明天就会干爆你。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Target sighted. Let's finish this and get payment from Ashvilli.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~发现目标。赶紧完事去找Ashvilli拿钱吧。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I always wanted to kill me a Russian.
~z~Get behind these cars. We must be hidden when they get here.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~躲在车后面。不能被他们直接发现。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Think about what I said to you. The offer will not be there forever.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~想想我跟你说的话。机会不是一直都有的。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I'd start running before we start shooting.
~z~Get out my face, you piece of shit.
~z~Timur? He is replaceable, but his death is part of the large failure.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~Timur？他是可以替换的，但他的死是这次巨大失败的一部分。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~You'd get the fuck out of here if you knew what was good for you.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~你他妈快滚出去，这是为了你好。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We will conceal ourselves. Place a bomb where they will not see it.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~我们要躲起来。把炸弹安到他们看不到的地方。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I'm glad I cheat my tax returns!
~z~We can't leave car like this. Straighten her.
~z~Make sure a bomb is well hidden. We shall be concealed here.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~确保炸弹藏好了。我们躲在这后面。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We've got to get rid of this attention.
~z~I'd prefer we weren't taking on the National Office of Security Enforcement, but that's a different matter.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~我可不想和国家安全办公室干上，不过那是另一回事了。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~ I expect more from a man of your reputation, Mr. Lopez. Goodbye.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~你辜负了你的名声，Lopez先生。再见了。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~This NOOSE team is in charge of half the drugs running in the city.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~这支NOOSE小队经营了市里一半的毒品生意。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~You're fucking with the wrong people, Russians.
~z~Place a bomb out of sight. We will hide here.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~在隐蔽处安放炸弹。我们要躲起来。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Take these sticky bombs, Luis. We will need them for our NOOSE friends.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~拿着这些黏弹，Luis。要用它来招待NOOSE的朋友们。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~You like getting your hands dirty, Mr. B?
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~你喜欢亲自动手干脏活吗，B先生？

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~What's so fucking funny, man? I don't get you.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~这有什么好笑的，哥们？搞不懂你。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Man, I guess shit just don't go to plan every time.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~哥们，有时候计划就是赶不上变化。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Good. Good. They should not see that until it's too late.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~好，很好。等他们发现就已经晚了。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We need to go down into the lot.
~z~Well done. It will be a fun treat for them.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~干得好。给他们准备一出恶作剧。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I don't think so. Maybe I hurt my hands hitting his head.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~也不一定。给他一下说不定骨折的是我。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Here are some makeshift bombs. They will be useful.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~拿上这些土制炸弹。会很有用的。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I see the target car. Let's set up this Russian and get out of here.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~看到目标车辆了。阴了这个俄国佬就赶紧撤退。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~~c~ Our Hispanic friend is really very useful.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~~c~我们的西班牙朋友真有用啊。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~The President said we can do whatever the fuck we want, assholes.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~总统说我们可以为所欲为，混蛋们。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Place a sticky bomb on the car.
~z~Well placed. The bomb should prove quite a surprise for our friends.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~安装的位置不错。炸弹会给我们的朋友一个大惊喜。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Let's drop this fucker and say he was an insurgent!
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~干掉这个混蛋，就说他想造反！

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We can't have this police attention. Lose it.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~我们不能被警察盯上。甩掉他们。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Stay down now. We shall wait for them.
~z~This is your excuse for parking? Straighten her up.
~z~Take us to the basement parking lot, in the Middle Park East.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~带我们去中心公园东的地下停车场。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We will die here if we do not fight. Come on. Let's go.

E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~我们被摆了一道！有袭击！有袭击！

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I hope you ain't deaf, 'cause I'm about to shoot you!
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~希望你没聋，我就要开枪打你了！

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We are looking for specific peace officers. Lose that heat.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~我们只想找那几个黑警。摆脱通缉。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Here. You will need these sticky bombs for the party.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~拿着。待会儿的狂欢会用到这些黏弹的。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Now, Luis, we see if you can handle yourself.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~好了，Luis，看看你是不是真的有两下子。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~I guess we got to move to plan B.
~z~Do you want them to see the explosive?
~z~We must remain hidden until they get here.
~z~Park the car straight. That will be suspicious.
~z~Get rid of these cops, Luis. We do not need extra eyes on us.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~甩掉这些条子，Luis。不能多一双眼睛盯我们。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~They called it in. More are coming!
~z~Keep your heads down until the party kicks off.
~z~We will use force if you don't vacate immediately.
~z~Get out of here, civilian. We don't want to start reading you the Jingoism Act.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~快点滚出去，平民。我不想给你念沙文主义法案。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Speak English, bro. I ain't feeling comfortable.
~z~Let's shoot this fuck and ask questions later. Just like the handbook says.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~先打死再说，之后才是询问。照手册上写的做。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~There is no plan B, you simpleton. Ray Bulgarin should not need to provide for failure.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~哪来的B计划，你这傻逼。Ray Bulgarin不需要失败时的预案。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Go to the garage off Topaz Street.
~z~Let's get out of here. Go. Go.
~z~That's the car. Get in and plant the evidence.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~就是这辆车。把证据放车里去。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Do not let your conscience worry you.
~z~Someone's fitted the vehicle with an IED. Search the area.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~有人在车上装了土制炸弹。搜索这片区域。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Put one of the bombs on the car and we shall wait for them.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~把炸弹安到车上，咱们等他们过来。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Look, man, I'm sorry about your friend, okay?
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~听我说，哥们。你朋友的事我很遗憾，好吧？
~z~你的接班人会收我的贿赂的。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~What do you wait for? Come on, Luis.
~z~Sir. You are going to have to leave the premises. We are on official N. O. O. S. E. business.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~先生，请你离开这座停车场。我们是国安办官方人员。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~The car's been rigged to blow. Scout the area for hostiles.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~车上安了炸弹。在这里搜寻敌人。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~This is the end of the line!
~z~Park up this spot by the pillar.
~z~~c~ Now you know what happens to the people who go against us.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~~c~这下知道跟我们对着干会有什么下场了吧。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Come on Luis, this is what we are born to do!
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~上吧Luis，这就是我们生来的使命。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~No money will buy us out of this, we have to lose them.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~花钱可没法买通追兵。只能甩掉他们。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Detonate when they are near the car.
~z~Things are about to get hot in here.
~z~There's a bomb on the car. Let's find the hostile that put it there. Move out.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~车上有炸弹。寻找敌人，当场击毙。散开。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Hey, civilian, you don't want to be around here. Move on out before we redact your ass.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~喂，平民，别在这里待着。不出去就让你人间蒸发。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~This will be nasty surprise for them, hide one of those sticky bombs on the car.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~给他们来点恶作剧，在车上藏几颗黏弹。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Mr. Ray is no here. Get him.
~z~Timur, bro. You ain't talking much. Nervous?
~z~Nothing worse than a bad guy with a badge.
~z~We have to fight our way out.
~z~Now we must hide and wait for our friends. Get behind a car.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~现在我们得躲着等朋友来。到车后面去。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Forward! We must fight out of here.
~z~They will see that there, you imbecile.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~放这里他们会看到的，傻逼吧你。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~When they gather round the car, blow it.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~等他们聚到车子周围了，引爆炸弹。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~Leave the car in this empty space over by the pillar.
~z~We're gonna get paid extra for killing you.
~z~Conceal yourselves behind these car. We will wait for Marki's puppets.
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~在车后躲好了。我们等着看Marki的傀儡吧。

E2BG1AU.original: ~z~We have not got Timur. What is this?
~z~Detonate when they come to the car, okay?
E2BG1AU.translated: ~z~他们一靠近车子就引爆，明白？
